write a program to check whether the given year is leap year or not

SOURCE CODE:

#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    // Write C code here
    int a;
    scanf("%d",&a);
    if(a%4==0 && a%100!=0 || a%400==0){
    printf("%d is leap year",a);
    }
    else{
    printf("%d is not a leap year",a);
    }
    return 0;
}

INPUT:
2100
2000
2004

OUTPUT:

2100 is not a leap year
2000 is leap year
2004 is leap year
